023 academic year: Tuesdays, in-person in the Student Employment Office (SSB 2100), 2PM – 4PM CST Thursdays, virtual via Zoom, 1PM-3PM CST Join the Zoom link below anytime. You will be entered into a waiting room and the advisor will let you in for a 1:1 session. Where: Virtual Zoom Link Meeting ID: 462 002 4241 Password: SEO2100! Make an appointment with us on Handshake Students can now schedule their own appointments for the Job Location, and Development program , resume review , and job search advice for part-time on/off campus positions with Student Employment staff directly on ! If you haven’t used Handshake before, you can log in to claim your account using your University credentials. Follow this link to schedule your appointment: Choose “Career Services”. Choose appointment type: On/Off Campus Student Employment Advising/Resume Review After that, you’ll receive an email confirmation with a Zoom link/location for the session.  If you would like a resume or cover letter review, just have those materials ready for the session.  For other topics, it would be helpful to come with a list of questions or issues you’d like to discuss with the advisor. Heading link xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"? Copy link Heading link xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"? Copy link National Student Employment Week, April 11-15, 2022 Posted on April 21, 2020 Sep 27 2022 Student Employment Drop-In Advising (In-Person) - Tuesdays, 2pm-4pm Sep 29 2022 Student Employment Drop-In Advising (Virtual) - Thursdays, 1pm-3pm Jan 10 2023 Spring 2023 Student Employment Drop-In Advising (In-Person) - Tuesdays, 2pm-4pm Jan 12 2023 Spring 2023 Student Employment Drop-In Advising (Virtual) - Thursdays, 1pm-3pm Jan 12 2023 Handshake- Take the First Step! University of Illinois Chicago Quick Links UIC Career Services UIC Careers For Students Job Listings JLD Program For Departments Forms Job Descriptions Student Wage Plan Footer Menu Students Departments Handshake UIC 